    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 in collector-tier condition. The S54 power plant remains a masterpiece of atmospheric induction, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously overhauled for optimal phase timing. This example retains its factory structural integrity with documented subframe reinforcement and fresh rod bearings, mitigating the chassis's known failure points. Power is delivered through a precise ZF 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring tactile feedback and linear torque distribution. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, utilizing refreshed bushings and dampening for a neutral handling profile. Finished in a flawless Laguna Seca Blue, this chassis exhibits zero oxidation and a mirror-like finish, representing the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s M-division engineering.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
